Dr. med. Andreas Becker is Head of the Department of Neurology and Medical Director at SRH Kurpfalz Hospital Heidelberg, Germany.
He is a board-certified neurologist and intensive care specialist with a particular focus on Parkinson’s disease, device-aided therapies, neurological intensive care medicine, and digital medicine.
Dr. Becker has led the Department of Neurology since 2014 and has served as Medical Director since 2018.
He is also actively involved in the education of Parkinson Nurses and in the development of national structures for Parkinson’s care in Germany.
